Q7 : write a command to revers the credit card numbers given below   

Input :
1234 5678 9101 1234  
2999 5178 9101 2234  
9999 5628 9201 1232  
8888 3678 9101 1232

Output :
1234 9101 5678 1234  
2234 9101 5178 2999  
1232 9201 5628 9999  
1232 9101 3678 8888 

Script Name : reverse_credit_card_numbers.sh
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

